These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: mirinda, hot-chocolate
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: soccer, volleyball
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: orchid, aconite
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Beverage       | hot-chocolate       | mirinda |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| Sport       | volleyball    | soccer    |
| Flower   | aconite       | orchid      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
There are 2 different favourite colors: black, lavender
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, time-travel
The people have 2 different hobbies: dancing, sudoku
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person who likes black is on the far left##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| Color           | black | lavender      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | action      |
| Hobby         | dancing | sudoku     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  librarian, photographer
2 different pets are kept: lizard, pony
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, country
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
1. the fan of country is on the left of the photographer##1
2. the librarian is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Job      | librarian | photographer  |
| Pet          | lizard    | pony   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   |
| Transport     | taxi     | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
