The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, quad-bike
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, security-guard
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, reading
1. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the person drinking soy-milk is the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea       | soy-milk |
| Transport          | quad-bike         | trike    |
| Job           | security-guard | nurse    |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks           | reading   |

