.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-9::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: may, july
There 2 different types of food: cucumber, spinach
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, chess
House: gothic-revival, colonial
1. the colonial house is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the person who's birthday is in july##1
3. the colonial house is on the left of the person who's hobby is chess##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| Birthday   | may         | july    |
| Food       | spinach     | cucumber  |
| Hobby      | board-games | chess     |
| House        | colonial     | gothic-revival |

