The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, sudoku
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: climbing, volleyball
There 2 different types of food: garlic, cabbage
1. the person eating cabbage is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the analyst##1
3. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who's sport is climbing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |
| Job           | analyst  | mechanic   |
| Hobby   | camping  | sudoku      |
| Sport         | climbing | volleyball |
| Food     | cabbage     | garlic |

