.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, security-guard
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: iris, bellflower
2 different games are played: scrabble, domino
The people use 2 different means of transport: bus, van
1. the coach is on the right of the person who growsiris##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person driving the van##1
3. the person playing scrabble is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | security-guard | coach     |
| Flower   | iris          | bellflower |
| Game           | scrabble          | domino    |
| Transport     | van            | bus       |

 